author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at how one of the two companies that make our graphics cards is now telling us that things will continue to get more expensive. It's not hard to see in some ways there is a case to be made that companies don't want us to easily have hardware in the future and would rather be constantly subscribed to hardware we never own. Why? Let's find out! Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
title: You Will Own Nothing, And You Will Be Happy...
